After Zhang Zhuang is over, it is highly recommended to do the final exercises since they contribute to the even distribution of qi in the body. Otherwise you may experience headaches, a burning sensation or distention in some areas or an uncomfortable condition. </i> </p>
<p> The time of day and the duration of each of the steps of the final exercises can be varied at their own discretion, depending on the sensations and the availability of time. Exercise 10 is optional.